{"nodes": [{"id": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp3_figs_exp3_digits_f8_boosting", "label": "F8 boosting chain \u2014 error vs depth, digits (gamma=0.68 bound)", "file_type": "image", "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp3\\figs_exp3_digits\\F8_boosting.png", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Left (log y): chain held error falls slightly and plateaus ~0.045-0.06 across 1-6 blocks (train error ~0.022-0.032, flat after block 2) against a steeply-falling e^(-1/2 T gamma^2), gamma=0.68 theoretical BoostResNet bound (dotted) \u2014 actual decay saturates far short of the bound after ~2 blocks. Right: per-block weak-edge gamma (residual variance explained) declines smoothly ~0.71->0.60, staying far above the dead-block line (~0.02) \u2014 no block dies, but each explains less residual, consistent with saturating (not exponential) boosting."}], "edges": [{"source": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp3_figs_exp3_digits_f8_boosting", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp3_experiment_3_doc", "relation": "references", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp3\\figs_exp3_digits\\F8_boosting.png", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp3_figs_exp3_digits_f8_boosting", "target": "draft6_0_research_papers_phase1_2_boostresnet_boosting", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.95, "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp3\\figs_exp3_digits\\F8_boosting.png", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp3_figs_exp3_digits_f8_boosting", "target": "draft6_0_src_stage1_report_boosting_chain", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp3\\figs_exp3_digits\\F8_boosting.png", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp3_figs_exp3_digit